data.description: Such a great ownership opportunity in Garrison Lakes!  Just off the I-70 corridor, you’ll enjoy this unique little lake community which is just minutes from Old Town Arvada (think popular dining, coffee shops, shopping!) and 15 minutes from both Downtown and Golden/Foothills (think easy escape to the mountains!).  This comfortable 2-story condo is adorned with brand new carpet throughout.  The main level boasts open living & dining areas with in-unit laundry and ½ bathroom on the main level for convenience.   The kitchen has been recently updated to include LVP flooring and granite counter tops along with stainless steel appliances. The wood-burning fireplace is perfect to enjoy with your weekend morning coffee or kick-back and relax after a hard day’s work.  Open up to the private balcony and enjoy the crisp fall air and vibrant colors. Upstairs, the primary bedroom features vaulted ceilings, a skylight and stretching windows to let the gorgeous, natural light in. The second bedroom is equally spacious with vaulted ceilings and the full bathroom is a perfect compliment to this upper level.  This community borders the Tomlinson Park with its idyllic setting and walking trails. We're also throwing in a $1500 concession at closing for bathroom upgrades + a 1-year home warranty so this unit is a perfect fit for anyone’s desire for a new start with a promise of low maintenance and care-free ownership! ALSO this property is located in a qualified census tract making it eligible for special financing incentives that are only offered through select lenders. Buyers may be eligible to receive a 2.5% credit of their loan amount that can be applied to reduce their interest rate and perhaps offset a portion of their closing costs.  Call Eric Sandefur at Sunflower Bank for more information 303-521-7658.
